      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
      "body" : "Arrays in .NET implement <code>IList</code> &amp; <code>ICollection</code> since .NET 1.1, and <code>IList&lt;T&gt;</code> and <code>ICollection&lt;T&gt;</code> since .NET 2.0. This is yet another case where Java is far behind the competition."
